      static <T extends Application<?,?>>
      T      		 WebFactory.getApplication(Class<T> appClass, String urlToBeLoaded)
      Common method that creates an instance of the application by default configuration - Configuration.byDefault Performs navigation to the required URL

      Supported WebDriver designations:
      - ESupportedDrivers.FIREFOX
      - ESupportedDrivers.CHROME
      - ESupportedDrivers.INTERNETEXPLORER
      - ESupportedDrivers.PHANTOMJS
      - ESupportedDrivers.SAFARI
      - ESupportedDrivers.REMOTE
      - ESupportedDrivers.ANDROID_CHROME
      - ESupportedDrivers.IOS_SAFARI
      All these should be defined in WebDriverSettings

      Presence of Capabilities is optional, except ESupportedDrivers.REMOTE, ESupportedDrivers.ANDROID_CHROME and ESupportedDrivers.IOS_SAFARI.
      static <T extends Application<?,?>>
      T      		 WebFactory.getApplication(Class<T> appClass, WebDriverEncapsulation wdEncapsulation, String urlToBeLoaded)
      Common method that creates an instance of the application by externally instantiated WebDriverEncapsulation Performs navigation to the required URL

      WebDriverEncapsulation should wrap instance of :
      - FirefoxDriver
      - ChromeDriver
      - InternetExplorerDriver
      - SafariDriver
      - PhantomJSDriver
      - RemoteWebDriver
      - AndroidDriver with capabilities like ExtendedDesiredCapabilities.androidChrome() supplemented by MobileCapabilityType.DEVICE_NAME
      - IOSDriver with capabilities like ExtendedDesiredCapabilities.iosSafari() supplemented by MobileCapabilityType.DEVICE_NAME and MobileCapabilityType.PLATFORM_VERSION
